review_blob: Eh, 8% alcohol and it gets you drunk.  Nice can too.  As far as tastes go it pretty much sucks but oh well.

9.99 for a 30-pack!  I dont care how bad this stuff is for that price.
Finish, texture, hops, barely and malt !
Ya know, this stuff is great for what it's intended for, getting drunk on a budget, so anyone who has any negatives about this beer shouldn't be drinking it in the first place.
This stuff is the bomb.  If you get the chance get some, it's the most delicious substance known to man.

This stuff is good, I bought it on sale for 5.99 a 12-pack and I'll definetely be getting it again.  It doesn't really taste like a "real" ice beer, its crisp and delicious and it gets you drunk without the fullness of Bud Ice.  I recommend.
Christ, you people are hard to convince, this stuff isn't bad at all for a full flavored lager and definetely up there with Heineken.  I'm diggin' it !
Let's face it, nobody drinks this stuff cuz it tastes good...but it is good at getting you drunk
